.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include <allegro.h>

.sp
.B int set_sound_input_source(int source);
.SH DESCRIPTION
Selects the audio input source. The parameter should be one of the values:

.nf
   SOUND_INPUT_MIC
   SOUND_INPUT_LINE
   SOUND_INPUT_CD
.fi
